{
  "page": "House Qo",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the city, see <a href=\"/index.php/Si_Qo\" title=\"Si Qo\">Si Qo</a>. For the God-Emperor, see <a href=\"/index.php/Pol_Qo\" title=\"Pol Qo\">Pol Qo</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold\">House Qo</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"><div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Regions</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Sweet_Lotus_Vale\" title=\"Sweet Lotus Vale\">Sweet Lotus Vale</a></li><li>(<a href=\"/index.php/Jhala\" title=\"Jhala\">Jhala</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a>)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nPrince(ss) of <a href=\"/index.php/Sweet_Lotus_Vale\" title=\"Sweet Lotus Vale\">Sweet Lotus Vale</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>House Qo</b> was a noble house from <a href=\"/index.php/Sweet_Lotus_Vale\" title=\"Sweet Lotus Vale\">Sweet Lotus Vale</a> on <a href=\"/index.php/Jhala\" title=\"Jhala\">Jhala</a>, the largest island of the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#House_Qo_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">House Qo at the end of the third century</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Historical_Members\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Historical Members</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Qo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Xanda_Qo\" title=\"Xanda Qo\">Xanda Qo</a> ended slavery on the Summer Isles and united all the islands under her rule. She was eventually followed as Princess of <a href=\"/index.php/Sweet_Lotus_Vale\" title=\"Sweet Lotus Vale\">Sweet Lotus Vale</a> by her daughter, <a href=\"/index.php/Chatana_Qo\" title=\"Chatana Qo\">Chatana Qo</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"House_Qo_at_the_end_of_the_third_century\">House Qo at the end of the third century</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Qo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: House Qo at the end of the third century\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The known Qos during the timespan of the events described in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Song_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A Song of Ice and Fire\">A Song of Ice and Fire</a></i> are:\n</p>\n<ul><li>no member has appeared yet.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Historical_Members\">Historical Members</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Qo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Historical Members\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Xanda_Qo\" title=\"Xanda Qo\">Xanda Qo</a>, Princess of <a href=\"/index.php/Sweet_Lotus_Vale\" title=\"Sweet Lotus Vale\">Sweet Lotus Vale</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Chatana_Qo\" title=\"Chatana Qo\">Chatana Qo</a>, her daughter and successor<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_Qo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafbeyond_the_free_cities:_the_summer_isles.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Beyond the Free Cities: The Summer Isles.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403101229\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.056 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.219 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 498/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10114/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4153/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 836/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1484/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.150/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.55 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  212.030      1 -total\n 82.20%  174.299      1 Template:Noble_House\n 81.68%  173.191      1 Template:Infobox\n 13.48%   28.590      1 Template:For-multi\n 13.24%   28.081      1 Template:Hatnote\n 11.24%   23.824     10 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.32%    7.036      3 Template:Ref\n  2.87%    6.083      2 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.86%    3.937      3 Template:Ref/core\n  0.81%    1.707      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26021-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403101229 and revision id 316241\n -->\n",
